import React from 'react';
import { Header, Icon, Segment, Grid, Embed, Modal, Button, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import Vikings from '../Video/Vikings.mp4';
import Got from '../Video/got.mp4';
import ReactPlayer from 'react-player'


const HeaderPart = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Grid columns="equal" inverted>
                <Grid.Row textAlign='right'>
                    <Grid.Column>
                        <Segment color='red' inverted>
                            <ReactPlayer url={Vikings}
                                //autoPlay
                                //playing
                                loop
                                width='100%'
                                controls
                                left="50%"
                            />
                        </Segment>
                    </Grid.Column>
                    <Grid.Column>
                        <Segment color='red' inverted>
                            <Button onClick={this.show('mini')}>Mini</Button>
                            <Button onClick={this.show('tiny')}>Tiny</Button>
                            <Button onClick={this.show('small')}>Small</Button>
                            <Button onClick={this.show('large')}>Large</Button>
                            <Button onClick={this.show('fullscreen')}>Fullscreen</Button>

                            <Modal size="100%" onClose={this.close}>
                                <Segment color='red' inverted>
                                    <ReactPlayer url={Vikings}
                                        //autoPlay
                                        //playing
                                        loop
                                        width='100%'
                                        controls
                                        left="50%"
                                    />
                                </Segment>
                                <Modal.Actions>
                                    <Button negative>No</Button>
                                    <Button
                                        positive
                                        icon='checkmark'
                                        labelPosition='right'
                                        content='Yes'
                                    />
                                </Modal.Actions>
                            </Modal>
                        </Segment>
                    </Grid.Column>
                </Grid.Row>
            </Grid>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default HeaderPart;
